Usage: set_property [-help] <object_list> <property_name> <property_value>
                    [-object_type <string>] [-quiet]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>             # List of objects on which property is to be appiled
                          # (string, required)
<property_name>           # Name of property (string, required)
<property_value>          # Value of property (string, required)
-object_type <string>     # Type of object on which property is to be defined.
                          # Types can be design, port, cell, pin, net, lib,
                          # lib_cell, lib_pin (string, optional)
-quiet                    # Specifies to exit quietly without issuing error
                          # (bool, optional)